---
title: Brown Sugar Bourbon & Pecan Salmon Elevated Dinners, Impressively Easy
description: Brown sugar? Amazing. Bourbon? Our fave. Salmon? Delish. On the table in 15 minutes? Please! You’ll sear salmon fillets to flaky perfection and top with a buttery, savory-sweet bourbon glaze and crunchy pecans. On the side are fragrant steamed jasmine rice and sautéed zucchini, for a quick, wholesome meal that’s packed with flavor.

